2015-01-13 Giancarlo Razzolini <grazzolini@gmail.com>

	* 0.0.2 :
	- The kernel parameters names changed. A new one was added, for setting up the device pre-connection.
	- There were missing modules that would prevent pppd from running. They were added to the installation.
	- Changes in the help and install texts.
	
2015-01-12 Giancarlo Razzolini <grazzolini@gmail.com>

	* 0.0.1 :
	- Initial release
	- Support for running a pppd daemon that dials out to a ppp(oe) provider, based on a kernel command line parameter
